.SH NAME
drm_crtc_legacy_gamma_set \- set the legacy gamma correction table
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" drm_crtc_legacy_gamma_set
.BI "(struct drm_crtc *crtc "  ","
.BI "u16 *red "  ","
.BI "u16 *green "  ","
.BI "u16 *blue "  ","
.BI "u32 size "  ","
.BI "struct drm_modeset_acquire_ctx *ctx "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "crtc" 12
CRTC object
.IP "red" 12
red correction table
.IP "green" 12
green correction table
.IP "blue" 12
green correction table
.IP "size" 12
size of the tables
.IP "ctx" 12
lock acquire context
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Implements support for legacy gamma correction table for drivers
that have set drm_crtc_funcs.gamma_set or that support color management
through the DEGAMMA_LUT/GAMMA_LUT properties. See
\fBdrm_crtc_enable_color_mgmt\fP and the containing chapter for
how the atomic color management and gamma tables work.

This function sets the gamma using drm_crtc_funcs.gamma_set if set, or
alternatively using crtc color management properties.
